cu.explanation_en: Setting the NGU IP to an unreachable address will cause GTP-U tunnel setup failure and prevent UPF communication.

du.explanation_en: Setting the downlink carrier frequency to match the SSB frequency creates misalignment and prevents proper carrier allocation and UE synchronization.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行載波頻率設定為與 SSB 頻率匹配會創建錯位，並阻止正確的載波分配和 UE 同步。
